<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Password Recovery%>
    </title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
        }

        .email-container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background-color: #FF6F61;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top-left-radius: 8px;
            border-top-right-radius: 8px;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .content a {
            color: #FF6F61;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="email-container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Password Recovery</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <%= firstName %>,</p>
            <p>We received a request to reset your password for your <%= companyName %> account.</p>
            <p>You can reset your password by clicking the link below:</p>
            <p><a href="<%= resetLink %>">Reset Password</a></p>
            <b><p>This link will only be available for an hour.</p></b>
            <p>If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email or contact support if you have
                questions.</p>
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p>The <%= companyName %> Team</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; <%= year %>
                    <%= companyName %>. All rights reserved.</p>
            <p>
                <%= companyAddress %>
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>